":0,"quote":{"pid":"88c022482cfb00aaec8e0474f8a241a4e8de4c6f","tid":2034620,"uid":217518,"like":65,"dislike":6,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335d161f00fa7723502e2a2c45994d435f3035d","tid":2034620,"uid":14054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"今日先閘撚住隻打尖的士狗<br />\n前面已經有三架專登貼哂線，慢流唔俾佢cut （前面嗰架都係的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n佢閘埋黎嗰下已經同我架車得返一隻手掌位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後面嗰架都最尾都俾佢cut到<br />\n<br />\n其實大家只要齊心慢流就可以唔撚俾佢cut<br />\n的士狗覺得難cut 慢慢又就肯排返隊杜絕呢啲情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8c164c63f4ea42fc845b4094ac0c7b946d82a6","tid":2034620,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"佢要攝咪比佢囉<br />\n十零廿秒姐<br />\n少好多爭執"},{"pid":"ec08a75a4898d9e485dbf56f857a577e36fb89c4","tid":2034620,"uid":126961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab404aab5418ca75e2ed164f25546cb6c40b0867","tid":2034620,"uid":66365,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"現實排隊既規矩係真係唔可以打尖，但揸車只要路面係虛線點解唔cut 得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"行車<br />\n<br />\n車輛應在行車綫之間行駛（由白色短虛綫劃分的兩條或多條行車綫）。除非有意超車、轉右或超越停放好的車輛，否則應在左綫行車。<br />\n<br />\n在接近危險的地方，可能有危險警告綫代替正常的行車綫界綫。除非情況安全，否則不得轉換行車綫。<br />\n<br />\n如非必要，不得隨便換綫。如駕駛人必須轉駛至另一條行車綫，首先須留意這樣做是否安全，並須緊記要用倒後鏡觀察後方。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如可安全轉綫，須先發出信號，並須確定不會逼使其他駕駛人突然轉向或減速。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遇到交通停頓或行車緩慢時，不得為趕前而強行切入另一條行車綫或超越前車。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/white_lines_and_traffic_lanes_/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fwhite_lines_and_traffic_lanes_%2Findex.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3mqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=f794c133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/white_lines_and_traffic_lanes_/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c7125213c103d3f718982031f043753cdf9a8bd","tid":2034620,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec08a75a4898d9e485dbf56f857a577e36fb89c4","tid":2034620,"uid":126961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab404aab5418ca75e2ed164f25546cb6c40b0867","tid":2034620,"uid":66365,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"現實排隊既規矩係真係唔可以打尖，但揸車只要路面係虛線點解唔cut 得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"行車<br />\n<br />\n車輛應在行車綫之間行駛（由白色短虛綫劃分的兩條或多條行車綫）。除非有意超車、轉右或超越停放好的車輛，否則應在左綫行車。<br />\n<br />\n在接近危險的地方，可能有危險警告綫代替正常的行車綫界綫。除非情況安全，否則不得轉換行車綫。<br />\n<br />\n如非必要，不得隨便換綫。如駕駛人必須轉駛至另一條行車綫，首先須留意這樣做是否安全，並須緊記要用倒後鏡觀察後方。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如可安全轉綫，須先發出信號，並須確定不會逼使其他駕駛人突然轉向或減速。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遇到交通停頓或行車緩慢時，不得為趕前而強行切入另一條行車綫或超越前車。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/white_lines_and_traffic_lanes_/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Froad_users_code%2Findex%2Fchapter_5_for_all_drivers%2Fwhite_lines_and_traffic_lanes_%2Findex.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3mqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=f794c133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/road_users_code/index/chapter_5_for_all_drivers/white_lines_and_traffic_lanes_